text: Bioko Norte is a province in Equatorial Guinea. The capital city is Rebola. The capital of the country is also in Bioko Norte. It is Malabo. It is on the northern part of the island Bioko. The southern part is named Bioko Sur. Part of the Pico Basil√© National Park is in Bioko Norte. Category:Provinces of Equatorial Guinea
